\fs32 \cf0 GOD\
\
1) Your have a purple path!\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our culture is hostile toward anything different or anyone who goes in a direction that is not with it\'85especially in political agenda\'92s.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92re called all kinds of names if you don\'92t line up with certain people\'92s thought process and the goal is to make you just like everyone else.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For this reason I remind you to fan into flame the gift of God, which is in you through the laying on of my hands.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For the Spirit God gave us does not make us timid,\'a0but gives us power,\'a0love and self-discipline.\'a0  2 Tim 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 	\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our culture continues to do this even when we are adults\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Oh you don\'92t watch that show?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Oh you\'92re still virgin?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Oh you don\'92t use bad language?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t look at other women?  What\'92s wrong with you?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why are you such a prude?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is when you try to fit something or someone into a situation they were not designed for it causes problems.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of me trying to fit my board into my fan that didn\'92t fit. (show pic of my windshield)\
\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we do this it distorts, bends, and ultimately weakens the integrity of the product or person!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have a bunch of weak Christians because they\'92ve changed and adjusted who they are so they can keep up with culture.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When you conform to culture you contort your character.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When you embrace your uniqueness you unleash your potential!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 2) You have a purple calling!\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf5 \super 9\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But you \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}BUT YOU!!!!  YOU ARE DIFFERENT\'85YOU ARE PURPLE\'85YOU ARE A WORLD CHANGER GOD IS WAITING TO UNLEASH ONTO THE WORLD\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf5 But you are a chosen people,\'a0a royal priesthood,\'a0a holy nation,\'a0God\'92s special possession\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How many of you were ever picked last at games growing up\'85it is a terrible feeling but here God says that isn\'92t what happened in the game of life.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Something hit me a few days ago as I was reading this.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do you know what the color of royalty is?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are a priest, a priestess; you are full of purple!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are fearfully and wonderfully made destined to do amazing things and God is waiting patiently to unleash you onto the world!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When you embrace your uniqueness you unleash your potential!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

