\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re going to continue that passage\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf5 \'85that you may declare the praises of him who called you out of darkness into his wonderful light.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Once you were not a people, but now you are the people of God;\'a0once you had not received mercy, but now you have received mercy.  1 Peter 2\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our job as a church is to LEAD PEOPLE into becoming PURPLE PEOPLE!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To lead them into the priesthood of God.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have a Purple Pastor\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m different than any pastor I\'92ve met in this town.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I have strengths and weakness that are unique to me.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of me wrestling with God about why He made me that way He did.  God\'92s answer was \'93Because if you\'92re going to reach a different type of person then you\'92ve got to be a different type of pastor\'94.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My job is to be the best Nic Smith I can possibly be\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When you embrace your uniqueness you unleash your potential!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1080\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
