\fs32 \cf0 Conclusion:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is not a sermon about being different for different sake.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is a message that God has put a unique calling on your life to be someone different inside\'85not just outside.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And in turn because of who you are on the inside, it causes you to proclaim from the rooftops who He is on the outside.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92ve got a unique series coming up in 4 weeks.  I want this to be our second Easter service.  \
